Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.85,ED1-Eng,,65,484,0,,{\fad(150,200)\blur3}Yeah, it's the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.23,ED1-Eng,,65,484,0,,{\fad(150,200)\blur3}Đừng hoảng sợ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:43.44,ED1-Eng,,65,484,0,,{\fad(150,200)\blur3}Hãy cùng tiến đến bên kia ngọn đồi
